25
00:01:27.979 --> 00:01:30.988
to go to business school, but I had,

26
00:01:30.988 --> 00:01:34.955
this was in the early
days of computers (laughs)

27
00:01:34.955 --> 00:01:38.311
and I had gotten interested in computers.

28
