I came to Stern, which was then
NYU Business School downtown

29
00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:47.200
and they had a little computer center,

30
00:01:47.209 --> 00:01:48.782
and I decided that I was gonna learn

31
00:01:48.782 --> 00:01:51.091
two things while I was there.

32
00:01:51.091 --> 00:01:54.260
