35
00:01:59.584 --> 00:02:01.972
I never did learn how
to touch type (laughs).

36
00:02:01.972 --> 00:02:03.523
Or maybe I did but I've forgotten now,

37
00:02:03.523 --> 00:02:05.545
and back to two finger pecking.

38
00:02:05.545 --> 00:02:07.886
But I became a self taught programmer,

39
00:02:07.886 --> 00:02:10.454
