40
00:02:10.454 --> 00:02:12.976
because I eventually became the director

41
00:02:12.980 --> 00:02:16.833
of the computer center,
while I was getting my PhD

42
00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:20.540
in Economics and Statistics at Stern.

43
