In 1973, the school formed
a department called

44
00:02:25.900 --> 00:02:29.060
Computer Applications
and Information Systems

45
00:02:29.060 --> 00:02:31.712
and I was one of the first faculty members

46
00:02:31.712 --> 00:02:35.879
in the department and I've
been here ever since (laughs).

47
00:02:35.879 --> 00:02:37.879
(music)

48
00:02:39.460 --> 00:02:45.140
My typical Monday is, I usually
get in around 11 o'clock

49
00:02:45.140 --> 00:02:47.700
and I do my email at home first,

50
00:02:47.705 --> 00:02:50.345
but I come in and I have
two classes on Monday.

51
00:02:50.345 --> 00:02:53.612
I have a class on design and development

52
00:02:53.612 --> 00:02:56.312
of web based systems at six o'clock.

53
00:02:56.320 --> 00:02:58.542
Two o'clock, I have a
dealing with data class.

54
00:02:58.542 --> 00:03:01.720
The class is based on Python notebooks,

55
00:03:01.720 --> 00:03:07.860
so we start with the
basics of Unix and Linux,

56
00:03:07.860 --> 00:03:10.534
just to get the students used to that.

57
00:03:10.534 --> 00:03:14.656
We move onto some Python,
some regular expressions,

58
00:03:14.660 --> 00:03:20.180
a lot of relational
databases, some Python Pandas,

59
00:03:20.180 --> 00:03:24.140
which is sort of like R
for Python, lets you do

60
00:03:24.140 --> 00:03:29.640
mathematical and statistical
calculations in Python.

61
00:03:29.640 --> 00:03:32.333
And then I end up with big data,

62
00:03:32.333 --> 00:03:35.102
for which, as you probably
know, I'm an evangelist.

63
00:03:35.102 --> 00:03:39.080
The students I have, weekly homeworks.

64
00:03:39.080 --> 00:03:42.180
I put them in teams and they
have to do a big project

65
00:03:42.181 --> 00:03:46.348
at the end of the term, and
they do some really cool things.

66
00:03:46.348 --> 00:03:48.348
(music)

67
00:03:49.328 --> 00:03:51.529
Yes, in fact, the whole course

68
00:03:51.529 --> 00:03:54.218
is taught using Jupyter notebooks.

69
00:03:54.218 --> 00:03:57.826
Every student has their
own virtual machine

70
00:03:57.826 --> 00:04:03.860
