that has all of the materials

72
00:04:07.837 --> 00:04:11.969
for the course either loaded
on it or in a Jupyter notebook,

73
00:04:11.969 --> 00:04:14.899
there are the commands to download it

74
00:04:14.900 --> 00:04:20.280
or update the server
with the right software.

75
00:04:20.280 --> 00:04:22.120
So everybody is in the same environment,

76
00:04:22.130 --> 00:04:24.332
it doesn't matter what kind of,

77
00:04:24.340 --> 00:04:26.099
whether they have a Mac
or a Windows machine

78
00:04:26.100 --> 00:04:31.360
